<p begin="24690000t" end="39590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="40700000t" end="73690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="74740000t" end="142430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="260590000t" end="303930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="304970000t" end="373350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="415410000t" end="496760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="517180000t" end="531510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="532530000t" end="565860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566890000t" end="618880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="619950000t" end="668980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="670000000t" end="730980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="800800000t" end="830720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第5話 策略&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="999330000t" end="1018670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;同學&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;什麼事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1019680000t" end="1057340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;其實我是來日本做秘密調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1058390000t" end="1088080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;請你別透露給日本警方…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1103760000t" end="1119000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;我明白了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1120110000t" end="1147410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;我不會對任何人提起你的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1148480000t" end="1160760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;當然也包括我父親&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1169830000t" end="1188830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;那麼…我先告辭了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1218550000t" end="1231170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;果然不出我所料&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1240230000t" end="1294270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;我也不想讓警方知道&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我和FBI探員接觸過&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1300960000t" end="1329290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;要是父親知道了,一定會告訴L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1337330000t" end="1364290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;這位仁兄完全沒有懷疑我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1365360000t" end="1383330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;剛才這裡所發生的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1384380000t" end="1410660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;會被警方當作普通意外處理&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1565560000t" end="1572840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;你回來了啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1584580000t" end="1593900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;我回來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1616940000t" end="1647200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;怎麼了,唉聲歎氣的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1648310000t" end="1661960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;發生什麼事了嗎?雷&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1683010000t" end="1712020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;碰巧被捲進公車劫持事件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1713040000t" end="1723960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;公車劫持事件?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1732390000t" end="1780060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;兩天前搶劫銀行的犯人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這次又劫持了公車&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1781110000t" end="1801700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;日本也變成危險的國家了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1813470000t" end="1846120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;你也搭上那輛公車了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1847170000t" end="1860140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;是啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1861190000t" end="1900780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;結果犯人跳下公車被車撞了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1914240000t" end="1933240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;那犯人死了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1939930000t" end="1978950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;可能吧,我沒看到最後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1979970000t" end="1989860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;雷&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2000660000t" end="2027960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;那真的是突發事件嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2034360000t" end="2048010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;什麼意思&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2049040000t" end="2085670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;你是為了調查某個人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;才坐上那輛公車的吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2086750000t" end="2111430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;而那犯人大概已經死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2118110000t" end="2132100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;那不就表示…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2133130000t" end="2142800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;我說啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2148810000t" end="2185100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;你過去的確是個優秀的FBI探員&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2186180000t" end="2212460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;但是現在只是我的未婚妻&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2222550000t" end="2242800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;已經不是探員了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2270930000t" end="2290610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;你答應過不插手KIRA事件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2291620000t" end="2314260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;不採取福險的行動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2315310000t" end="2373330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;所以我才帶你一起&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;來探望你在日本的父母&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2379040000t" end="2395990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;我知道了,雷&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2397060000t" end="2423000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;不小心老毛病又犯了,對不起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2437430000t" end="2464390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;我也不對,你別那麼在意&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2465460000t" end="2478770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;等我們有了家庭&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2479810000t" end="2516780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;你會忙得忘記自己當過探員&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2517840000t" end="2540480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;連犯老毛病的時間都沒有了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2560890000t" end="2569530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;話說回來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2570560000t" end="2603210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;還是幫我想想怎麼問候你老爸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2604260000t" end="2617230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;才能讓他對我更有好感&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2649310000t" end="2695270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;馬上就把白天那位探員名字&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;寫上去嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2696360000t" end="2732990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;不,一周後再寫他的名字&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2738060000t" end="2755010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;如果剛見完面他就死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2756080000t" end="2774730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;嫌疑會落到我的頭上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2775770000t" end="2798070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;等他的搜查更有進展&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2799120000t" end="2835410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;調查過更多警方相關人員之後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;再寫比較好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2836500000t" end="2884850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;暫時還是拿牢裡的罪犯開刀&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;讓L去煩惱吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2902560000t" end="2910180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2924250000t" end="2966230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;又出現寫下類似遺書的犧牲者了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2967290000t" end="2978890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;把畫面傳過來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3009330000t" end="3020590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;死神是…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3036700000t" end="3073330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;L,知道嗎?死神是…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3089410000t" end="3118080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;你想說死神是存在的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3126790000t" end="3158070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;渡,通知警方&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3159150000t" end="3180760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;隨時注意牢內的動靜&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3181840000t" end="3218130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;以後可能還會出現這類訊息&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3219210000t" end="3231490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3325650000t" end="3368650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;人好多,要在這裡動手嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3369690000t" end="3422020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;我會讓你見識這幾天調查&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;和各種測試的成果&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3423080000t" end="3432750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;測試?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3446770000t" end="3483060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;利用死亡筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;以各種殺人方式&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3484140000t" end="3506090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;來對付這一帶的罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3512840000t" end="3545490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;先在死亡筆記本上&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;寫下死因和死亡過程&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3546540000t" end="3579190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;之後再寫下名字,也能照樣實現&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3599590000t" end="3616880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;這件事連我都不知道&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3626620000t" end="3655630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;來了,時間剛剛好&#x202c;</p>
