<p begin="11586570000t" end="11608870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle281">&#x202a;這樣他無法放心的進行指揮&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11609930000t" end="11654530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle282">&#x202a;也就是說,L是等著總部中&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;留下願意冒死反抗罪惡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11655640000t" end="11693300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle283">&#x202a;而且是足以讓他信任的人嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11725040000t" end="11757010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle284">&#x202a;總之,要和L聯手的話,我就退出&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11765420000t" end="11814450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle285">&#x202a;請放心,我不會跟蹤大家&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也不會去找L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11833820000t" end="11872500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle286">&#x202a;我願意相信L,和他合作看看&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11880530000t" end="11889850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle287">&#x202a;我也願意&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11930910000t" end="11964580000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle288">&#x202a;我目前在帝東飯店的房間內&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="11972290000t" end="12007560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle289">&#x202a;以後將每隔幾天&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就搬到都內其他飯店&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12008660000t" end="12054620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle290">&#x202a;今後請將那間飯店房間&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;當做真正的搜查總部&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12061380000t" end="12088000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle291">&#x202a;如果願意在此條件下合作&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12089070000t" end="12130030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle292">&#x202a;請分為兩組,相隔半小時以上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12131110000t" end="12161710000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle293">&#x202a;在凌晨12點之前到這裡來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12198510000t" end="12244470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle294">&#x202a;KIRA,可以這麼說吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12245560000t" end="12270810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle295">&#x202a;現階段的你我仍算是旗鼓相當&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12278930000t" end="12333540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle296">&#x202a;好吧,我就首次以L的身份現身吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12347660000t" end="12383610000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle297">&#x202a;如果你得知這個消息的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12384700000t" end="12407340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle298">&#x202a;一定會接近我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12416400000t" end="12430390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle299">&#x202a;那就正合我意了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12451770000t" end="12480100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle300">&#x202a;這幾天,我的行動很頻繁&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12489140000t" end="12519740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle301">&#x202a;仔細想想,有沒有閃失&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12520840000t" end="12551780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle302">&#x202a;還有,今後要怎麼行動&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12573560000t" end="12605870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle303">&#x202a;現在起才是真正的戰鬥,L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12683000000t" end="12708940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle304">&#x202a;請進來吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12805120000t" end="12855060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle305">&#x202a;看見誰都無法看見的夢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12856170000t" end="12909870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle306">&#x202a;捨棄所有不需要的事物&#x202c;</p>
